OL,10,Fby Gordon Rollings.
OL,11,
OL,12,CG1974FThe 19th Eurovision Song Contest
OL,13,Fairs on BBC One, live from The Dome,
OL,14,FBrighton.
OL,15,
OL,16,FKatie Boyle presented, with David Vine
OL,17,Fproviding the commentary.
OL,18,
OL,19,FOlivia Newton-John was joint-4th for
OL,20,Fthe UK and Sweden's Abba famously won
OL,21,Fwith Waterloo.
